"The smell is wheat, mango, a little honey, citrus and malt.  The mango is the most dominant smell with just a tad bit of alcohol.  The flavor is mango, citrus tartness, earthy wheat and citrus.  The mouthfeel is fizzy and a bit puckering like a wild ale.  It does drink much better than 10%, but you have to really like mango to be into this one."
